{"tid":715234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA追究瑞士孖寶做政治手勢","createTime":"2018-06-24T10:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T11:51:06.000Z","uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1ab55c4d21f8d59d9a997ca1fbb7d7f1264bec","tid":715234,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=1SWaFfpca83OCmV2nzhWpNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=18dcf5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】瑞士孖寶梳頓沙基利、格列沙加上場對塞爾維亞入球後做出政治手勢，或被國際足協判罰。<br />\n<br />\n國際足協週六發出聲明，證實會追究梳頓沙基利（Xherdan Shaqiri）、格列沙加在週五以2:1反勝塞爾維亞的世界盃E組次輪比賽中做出政治手勢一事：「FIFA紀律委員會已就兩人的慶祝動作，展開了紀律聆訊。」<br />\n<br />\n科索沃與塞爾維亞的關係一直緊張，前者於2008年獨立後，塞爾維亞一直拒絕承認其獨立地位；<span style=\"color: red;\">而沙基利、格列沙加同為科索沃裔、阿爾巴尼亞族的瑞士人，因此在國仇家恨之下，慶祝入球時做出代表阿爾巴尼亞雙頭鷹的手勢。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於塞爾維亞球迷在該場比賽中，展示涉及政治的標語，FIFA亦向塞爾維亞足總展開調查。而塞爾維亞教練卡斯達積在該仗賽後的言論，FIFA亦會作出追究。</span>"},{"pid":"e7feb207bc5010e48b12fd9ac8c63205321ae9bc","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢地又科索沃又阿爾巴尼亞，點解代表瑞士而又唔係前兩者？"},{"pid":"14ede5a446a24a54a98f4c17feea4af3fcda788e","tid":715234,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"如果係尼馬做 會唔會受罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96ecb08181f9fecdb9da1a84b9870809be26a1e","tid":715234,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"尼馬做同樣動作既話 會唔會受罰"},{"pid":"bbfa3f8eb9f1202ead7f2897e5223b63bfa55057","tid":715234,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7feb207bc5010e48b12fd9ac8c63205321ae9bc","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢地又科索沃又阿爾巴尼亞，點解代表瑞士而又唔係前兩者？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"因內戰冇返科索沃，留咗係瑞士既難民後代"},{"pid":"75debe81ff8aae087408540c74a66ad804c6e6fe","tid":715234,"uid":26862,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e7feb207bc5010e48b12fd9ac8c63205321ae9bc","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢地又科索沃又阿爾巴尼亞，點解代表瑞士而又唔係前兩者？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"安全"},{"pid":"0ee5de17961828c4c4a69edf4daa3e96b5b4621c","tid":715234,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"咁球埸內D中國國旗呢?"},{"pid":"da37ddd5b2dd489fe44ba6d786723497451db8cc","tid":715234,"uid":103035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7feb207bc5010e48b12fd9ac8c63205321ae9bc","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢地又科索沃又阿爾巴尼亞，點解代表瑞士而又唔係前兩者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"佢地代表過瑞士踢國家隊<br />\n科索沃同阿爾巴尼亞獨立之後FIFA唔俾佢地改"},{"pid":"2a2a8f44ff30394364ed852908f5ca1498c79ab0","tid":715234,"uid":28808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ee5de17961828c4c4a69edf4daa3e96b5b4621c","tid":715234,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"咁球埸內D中國國旗呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"或成最後贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8400bde34473c92e24ae8c9d7e845af8b80ead29","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da37ddd5b2dd489fe44ba6d786723497451db8cc","tid":715234,"uid":103035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7feb207bc5010e48b12fd9ac8c63205321ae9bc","tid":715234,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢地又科索沃又阿爾巴尼亞，點解代表瑞士而又唔係前兩者？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"佢地代表過瑞士踢國家隊<br />\n科索沃同阿爾巴尼亞獨立之後FIFA唔俾佢地改"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:58:46.000Z",